project_name: IVP_LR_Connect
label: IVP_LR_Connect
description: |
  This demonstration illustrates the proper setup of a star network topology, enabling bidirectional communication between the Sink and Sensor nodes. The PB0 pushbutton serves to enable or disable sleep mode, in conjunction with adjusting the VCOM option for 'reception while sleeping'.
category: Connect Examples
